    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "topo_text",
      "x": 950,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 195,
      "text": "registry.load_all(modules_config)\n\n1. Instantiate all registered modules\n2. Read each module.dependencies\n3. Build adjacency + in_degree map\n4. Kahn's BFS: enqueue zero-in-\n   degree nodes (sorted for det.)\n5. Process batch: append to sorted,\n   decrement neighbour in-degrees\n6. Repeat until queue empty\n7. If remaining > 0: cycle error\n\nResult: deps always before dependents",
      "originalText": "registry.load_all(modules_config)\n\n1. Instantiate all registered modules\n2. Read each module.dependencies\n3. Build adjacency + in_degree map\n4. Kahn's BFS: enqueue zero-in-\n   degree nodes (sorted for det.)\n5. Process batch: append to sorted,\n   decrement neighbour in-degrees\n6. Repeat until queue empty\n7. If remaining > 0: cycle error\n\nResult: deps always before dependents",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
