      "y": 760,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 145,
      "text": "FATAL (stop startup):\n• Missing required env credentials\n• Runtime binary not on PATH\n• Circular module dependencies\n• DB provisioning failure\n\nNON-FATAL (disable module):\n• Module config schema invalid\n• Module migration fails\n• Module credentials missing\n• Module on_startup() raises\n• Module tool registration fails\n\nOn fatal error: call on_shutdown()\non all already-started modules",
      "originalText": "FATAL (stop startup):\n• Missing required env credentials\n• Runtime binary not on PATH\n• Circular module dependencies\n• DB provisioning failure\n\nNON-FATAL (disable module):\n• Module config schema invalid\n• Module migration fails\n• Module credentials missing\n• Module on_startup() raises\n• Module tool registration fails\n\nOn fatal error: call on_shutdown()\non all already-started modules",
